title: Doms Stereo Oldies Remixes
description:
Here are some of my remixes, all in the FLAC format.  You may need a plug-in to play these files.

Here is what is included:


Playlist files:

      1. 409(doms Stereo Mix) (1:57)
      2. Darlin (Doms Wide Mix) (2:06)
      3. Good Vibrations(doms Stereo Mix) (4:06)
      4. Surfer Girl (Doms Wide Stereo Mix) (2:15)
      5. Wouldn't It Be Nice (Doms Stereo Take 21 Mix) (2:34)
      6. Wouldn't It Be Nice (Mike and Brian Final Mix) (2:32)
      7. I Saw Her Standing There (Doms Stereo Version No Claps) (2:56)
      8. I Wanna Hold Your Hand (Doms Stereo Mix1) (2:23)
      9. I'll Get You (Doms Stereo Mix1) (2:04)
      10. Love Me Do (Dominicks Stereo Remix) (2:17)
      11. Maxwell's Silver Hammer (Doms Stereo1) (3:24)
      12. She Loves You (Doms Stereo Instrumental) (2:18)
      13. She Loves You (Doms Stereo Mix1) (2:18)
      14. She Loves You (Doms Stereo Mix2) (2:18)
      15. Taxman (Doms Mix1) (2:26)
      16. Little Darlin (Doms Stereo Mix) (2:08)
      17. Madonna - Into the groove (Doms Remix) (7:36)
      18. Moonglow (Doms Stereo Mix) (3:25)
      19. Mr Sandman (Doms Stereo Mix) (2:34)
      20. Rolling Stones - The Last Time (3:42)
      21. She's Something Else (doms Stereo2) (2:32)
      22. The Who - My Generation [Doms Stereo OVERDUB Mix) (3:20)

Enjoy!

Dominick
